        <item>
            <title>【評測】小米 S Mini LED 65 2025 開箱評測，預載 Google TV OS 可裝 APP + QD – Mini LED 面板亮度對比度更勝從前 + 設計走平實路線風格一般</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/17/mi-sminiled652025-review/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mi-sminiled652025-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/17/mi-sminiled652025-review/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 14:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[家居無線]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音產品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[評測]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mi]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mi S Mini LED 2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智能顯示屏]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1281998</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>去到年底，不少品牌都紛紛推出自家的新一代電視，小米早前亦推出了新一代，採用全新 QD – Mini LED 面板的智能顯示屏：小米 S Mini LED 2025，筆者就借得它的 65 吋版本，究竟採用新面板的這部智能顯示屏表現如何？就讓 Edward 為 unwire.hk 讀者們實測一下吧。</p><h2>為何稱「智能顯示屏」？內有原因</h2><p>眾所周知，小米在香港早已有推出智能電視產品，但今次推出的小米 S Mini LED 65 2025 為何稱為「智能顯示屏」而非「智能電視」？其實原因只有一個，就是因為它沒有內建電視調頻器（TV Tuner），直接點説就是沒有內建電視天線，換言之大家是不能將天線插入它並欣賞電視訊號直播的，與之前推出的小米電視系列是有不同，這一點大家在入手時一定要留意。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282006" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mi_002-694x303.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="303" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mi_002-694x303.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mi_002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282007" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mi_001-694x215.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="215" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mi_001-694x215.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mi_001.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲上面兩個擷自官方規格的部分，第一張是來自小米電視，而第二張是來自今次這部小米智能顯示屏，大家可以見到智能顯示屏確實寫著未設天線接口，而小米電視就設有 ATV / DTMB 調諧器，這就是為何今次這件新產品並非稱為智能電視而是智能顯示屏的主因。</p><h2>預載 Google TV OS 彌補沒內建天線損失</h2><p>雖然如此，但大家依然可以透過小米 S Mini LED 65 2025 欣賞電視直播，原因是它是內建了 Google TV OS 的智能顯示器，它內建了 Play Store 商店，用家只要透過 Play Store 就可以安裝不同電視台的自家 APP，筆者試用過，由電視台的 myTV Super（TVB）、ViuTV，到串流影片平台 Netflix、Disney+、YouTube 等都可以安裝及使用得到，尤其是電視台的 APP，只要註冊後就可以欣賞電視直播，與大家在手機、平板或電腦上瀏覽電視直播方法是一樣的，雖然相比接收天線訊號會有少許延遲（大約 10 多 20 秒左右），但相信對於絕大部分用家來説，應該也不會太介意吧。不過最重要是預載了 Google TV OS 可以直接裝 APP，令大家無需再接駁 TV Stick 已可用到智能電視的功能，變相省回一個 HDMI 端子可以接駁其他裝置，使用上亦更加方便。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282009" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_121845-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_121845-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_121845.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲S Mini LED 2025 預載了 Android TV 14 版本的 Google TV OS，不像之前小米推出的智能電視般需要插入 TV Stick 才可以進入 Google TV 安裝軟件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282010" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_121048-694x416.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="416" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_121048-694x416.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_121048.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲S Mini LED 2025 的主介面採用了近乎原生的 Google TV 介面，而操控只需要透過附送的遙控器即可。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282011" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123511-694x402.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="402" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123511-694x402.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123511.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282012" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123336-694x404.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="404" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123336-694x404.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123336.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲雖然沒有電視天線，但透過 Google TV，就已可通過不同電視台的 APPS，欣賞各大電視台的電視直播，不過比較可惜的是暫時只可欣賞 TVB 及 ViuTV，有線的開電視及香港電台就由於沒有相關 APPS，所以就未能在此電視上欣賞直播了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282024" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204908-694x403.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="403" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204908-694x403.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204908.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282025" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205045-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205045-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205045.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲筆者試過透過 myTV Super 及 ViuTV APP 欣賞兩個電視台的直播，是完全沒有問題的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282018" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/002-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/002-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/002.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282019" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/001-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/001-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/001.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲當然要解決此問題亦不難，由於 S Mini LED 2025 支援 Miracast 無線投影功能，大家只需要在手機或平板開啟開電視或 RTHK 的 APP，之後使用 Miracast 無線投屏到智能顯示屏上，就可以間接在大熒幕欣賞這兩個電視台的電視直播了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282020" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205345-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205345-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205345.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282021" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205435-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205435-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205435.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282023" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204342-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204342-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204342.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282022" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_122643-694x408.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="408" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_122643-694x408.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_122643.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲當然作為支援安裝 APPS 的平台，要在 S Mini LED 2025 上欣賞 Netflix、Disney+、Max、甚至欣賞 Now TV 收費電視頻道的節目也可以，而由於顯示屏本身支援 4K 解析度及 Dolby Vision 格式，所以欣賞相關格式影片自然亦沒問題。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282031" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204502-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204502-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204502.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲遙控本身亦設有 Netflix、YouTube 及 Amazon Prime Video 的獨立啟動鍵，亦可按下 APPS 按鍵進入程式列表。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282026" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205336-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205336-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205336.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282027" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205511-694x395.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="395" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205511-694x395.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205511.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲筆者實測欣賞 Netflix 及 Disney+ 上的串流影片，流暢度十分高，畫質亦十分不錯。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282028" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123248-694x420.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="420" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123248-694x420.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123248.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲以 Now TV APP 欣賞英超直播亦完全無難度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282029" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123629-694x408.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="408" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123629-694x408.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123629.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282030" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123635-694x408.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="408" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123635-694x408.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123635.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，用家亦可安裝 VLC for Android 或 MX Player，瀏覽抄寫到電視內或接駁到電視的 USB 手指內的本地影片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282032" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123607-694x418.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="418" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123607-694x418.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123607.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲除了影片平台外，其實用家亦可安裝其他多媒體平台，例如：可以安裝 Spotify 或 KKBOX 欣賞音樂，或者安裝不同 Tuner 程式收聽電台節目。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282033" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205631-694x409.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="409" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205631-694x409.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205631.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲透過 Tunein Radio 就已可收聽香港電台的直播節目。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282034" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205713-694x414.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="414" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205713-694x414.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205713.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282035" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205731-694x409.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="409" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205731-694x409.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205731.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲筆者亦試過在顯示屏上收聽 Spotify 音樂，甚至可以開啟「歌詞」功能，大家就可以與親友在大熒幕上唱 K 了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282037" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123652-694x417.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="417" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123652-694x417.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123652.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲筆者亦發現大家可以在智能顯示屏上安裝 VPN 軟件，暫時見到有 NordVPN 及 SurfShark 兩個較熱門的選擇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282038" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_212856-694x394.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="394" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_212856-694x394.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_212856.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282039" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213544-694x401.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="401" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213544-694x401.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213544.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282040" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213232-694x411.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="411" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213232-694x411.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213232.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲筆者試過在 S Mini LED 2025 上可以成功使用 VPN APP 連線到美國或英國等其他國家的伺服器，之後就可以看到香港睇不到，但在其他國家可以看到的節目。例如：在英國 Netflix 上可以看到 Harry Porter 電影，但筆者發現在香港的 Netflix 上就看不到了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282041" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_212959-694x409.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="409" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_212959-694x409.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_212959.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282042" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213218-694x410.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="410" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213218-694x410.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213218.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外要知道是否成功使用 VPN 連線並進入海外的 Netflix 伺服器十分簡單，只需要看影片簡介上方的評級標誌就可以了：第一張是美國的，第二張就是英國的。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
